# Project Shell

- For Bash, sh, makepkg, pacman, and other POSIX/MSYS package commands in this
  workspace, use the `MSYS2-CYGWIN-STAGE3` terminal profile from
  `.vscode/settings.json`.
- The shell executable is
  `D:/CI-Tools/msys64-stage3/msys64/usr/bin/bash.exe` with `--login -i`.
- Before invoking `bash` from another terminal, mirror `build-all.bat` and
  prepend `D:\CI-Tools\msys64-stage3` and
  `D:\CI-Tools\msys64-stage3\msys64\usr\bin` to `PATH`.
- Set `MSYS=winsymlinks:native`, `MSYSTEM=CYGWIN`, and `CHERE_INVOKING=1`.
- Do not use bare `bash` or `sh` from the Windows `PATH` for this repo; it may
  resolve to WSL instead of the configured MSYS2/CYGWIN environment.
